children.label: getCreateControlButton
description: Returns a button that allows controls to be created externally using the embeddable

children.label: closePopover
description: Closes the create control menu popover when flyout opens - only necessary if `buttonType === 'toolbar'`

returnComment:
If `buttonType == 'toolbar'`, returns `EuiContextMenuPanel` with input control types as items.
Otherwise, if `buttonType == 'callout'` returns `EuiButton` with popover containing input control types.

children.label: getToolbarButtons
description: Returns the toolbar button that is used for creating controls and managing control settings

children.label: by_type
signature: { [key: string]: { total: number; details: { [key: string]: number; }; }; }

misc.label: PersistableControlGroupInput
description: Only parts of the Control Group Input should be persisted

misc.label: SerializableControlGroupInput
description: Some use cases need the Persistable Control Group Input to conform to the SerializableRecord format which requires string index signatures in any objects
